This is a C programming language package tuned for the Tandy Color Computer. This worked is based off the GCC6809 being worked on Brian Dominy at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.oddchange.com/gcc6809/"}}{\fldrslt GCC6809 - C compiler for the 6809 processor}}. You should become familiar with the compiler he provides, because this document will only describe the changes made for the Color Computer.\
\

\f0\b\fs28 Supported hosts.
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\
Currently I provide binaries for Mac OS X and CYGWIN. CYGWIN is a unix like environment for Windows.\
\

